{% set description %}
  The variant card prop can turn a teaser into a teaser card.
{% endset %}

{% set notes %}
  <bolt-ol>
    <bolt-li>By setting the <code>variant</code> prop to <code>card</code> the teaser can become a teaser card.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>When the <code>variant</code> prop is set to <code>card</code> it's possible to apply spacing around the teaser and rounding the teaser's corners.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>Reference <a href="{{ link['viewall-components-teaser'] }}?selected-tab=schema" class="e-bolt-text-link">the schema</a> for <code>spacing</code> and <code>border_radius</code> props.</bolt-li>
  </bolt-ol>
{% endset %}

